oodie Forms data immutable and performant to work with.",[130,150,154],{"icon":151,"target":133,"title":152,"to":153},"goodie:brand-evilmartians","Nano Events","https://github.com/ai/nanoevents","Simple and tiny event emitter library for JavaScript. Gives Goodie Forms power to emit and listen to certain events.",[114,156,158],{"id":157},"key-features","Key Features",[160,161,162,169,179,207,213,219],"ul",{},[163,164,165,168],"li",{},[109,166,167],{},"Framework-agnostic core",": Designed to work with any UI layer (React, Vue, Solid, or vanilla).",[163,170,171,174,175,178],{},[109,172,173],{},"Fully type-safe",": Built with ",[103,176,140],{"href":141,"rel":177},[107]," from the ground up. Deep type inference ensures form values, errors, and validation are correctly typed at every level.",[163,180,181,184,185,189,190,195,196,195,201,206],{},[109,182,183],{},"Validation library agnostic",": Thanks to ",[103,186,188],{"href":135,"rel":187},[107],"Standard Schema",", you can plug in popular libraries like ",[103,191,194],{"href":192,"rel":193},"https://zod.dev/",[107],"Zod",", ",[103,197,200],{"href":198,"rel":199},"https://valibot.dev/",[107],"Valibot",[103,202,205],{"href":203,"rel":204},"https://github.com/jquense/yup",[107],"Yup",", or your own validation logic without being locked into a single solution.",[163,208,209,212],{},[109,210,211],{},"Fine-grained control over state",": Track touched, dirty, validating, and error states per field or per form.",[163,214,215,218],{},[109,216,217],{},"Optimized for DX",": Clear APIs, strong IntelliSense support, and predictable behavior reduce cognitive load during development.",[163,220,221,224],{},[109,222,223],{},"Unopinionated by default",": No forced UI components. No design constraints. Goodie Forms handles logic — you handle presentation.",[127,226,227,232],{},[130,228,231],{"icon":229,"target":133,"title":230,"to":105},"mdi:github","Goodie Forms - GitHub Monorepo","GitHub repository that hosts the source code of Goodie Forms and its subpackages.",[130,233,237],{"icon":234,"target":133,"title":235,"to":236},"mdi:discord","Discord Server Invite","https://discord.gg/KNxxdvN","Invite to the Discord Server",{"title":239,"searchDepth":240,"depth":240,"links":241},"",2,[242,243],{"id":116,"depth":240,"text":117},{"id":157,"depth":240,"text":158},"Welcome to Goodie Forms documentation.","md",null,{},{"icon":14},{"title":11,"description":250},"Discover Goodie Forms, a modern TypeScript form state and data management library. Framework-agnostic, validation-agnostic, and built for full control, performance, and developer experience.","mwyLOZ-6jhZKNc0tgJAHim7vwS8FUT_P-Q8qK-IITYQ",[246,253],{"title":16,"path":17,"stem":18,"description":254,"icon":19,"children":-1},"The architectural principles behind Goodie Forms",1772225555181]